# radroots_replica_sync_wasm

Wasm bindings for replica synchronization interfaces in Rad Roots data layers.

## Goals

- define stable wasm bindings for replica sync and ingest flows
- keep request parsing and result marshaling deterministic in web runtimes
- support integration with wasm SQL executor surfaces
- provide reusable sync bridge primitives for higher-level Rad Roots crates

